messages.message:
Oh, I forgot to send updates about Cypress last week:
• `workspace-settings` fixed with @Xindi Xu’s PR: https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/69792
    ◦ We weren’t clearing the cache key after creating a workspace, causing a search to fail
• `aihub-project-migration` fixed PR: https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/69818
    ◦ We didn’t check if we were currently in an org before switching to it. We always assumed we were in a different org.
    ◦ This is moved to non-blocking anyway, it seemed like the fix wasn’t working and I need more time to investigate.
• `view-home-page.spec.ts` is fixed PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/69960/files#diff-29f0085de74c1ef3830fb9d379104dda303441a699089b94b7d2f12d3e085bd5)
    ◦ We renamed some buttons on the homepage.
• We have a WIP of running Cypress tests ibdev-backend PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/69972)
    ◦ We were running into issues during testing since the `ibdev-backend` was broken last week. Thread (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C05L87V014J/p1745251217269009).
    ◦ Currently on pause until next week when I get more time.
